  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ne možete koristiti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">didn't</span> sa nekim glagolima da napravite negativne rečenice u prošlom vremenu. Jedan primer je glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to be</span>.</p>\n<p>Ako želiš da napraviš negativnu rečenicu koristeći glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to be</span> u prošlom vremenu, samo dodaj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">not</span> nakon <span class=\"highlighted-text\">was</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">were</span>. Na primer:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pozitivan</th>\n<th>Negativan</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">It was working normally.</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">It wasn't working normally.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">They were informed earlier.</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">They weren't informed earlier.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Wasn't</span> je skraćenica od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">was not</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">weren't</span> je skraćenica od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">were not</span>.</p>\n</section>",
